_header: This day Saint Luke telleth us
Note: For other MSS see 6047; for the version in the ‘expanded’ Cycle see 4687.
_description: Gospel for Second Sunday in Advent, in the Northern Homily Cycle

CULDd11.First Lines:
This day seynt luke telliþ vsin oure gospel þat
                    ihesus…
CULDd11.Last Lines:
…Of o toknyng I haue hard telleþat falliþ wel to
                    oure gospelle
CULDd11.Attributed Title:
Erunt signa in sole & luna & cetera (f.
                    42v)
